                    C O N T R O L S  E X P L A I N E D

  Controls:

  During the game, if you press the <F1> key, a list of controls will
  appear.

  For all you people out there who are unable to do this (Well, maybe
  your <F1> key doesn't work), here's how it works:

  During the Game:

  MOVE BEASTIE LEFT              : Left Arrow key of Joystick left
  MOVE BEASTIE RIGHT             : Right Arrow key of Joystick right
  MAKE BEASTIE JUMP              : Either <Shift> or the <Ctrl> key or
                                   (BLUE) CD남 Joypad button!

  Note: During a jump, unlike "Worms", you can control which way you drift.
        The little Beastie dudes are more advanced then little pink Worms
        see.

  SCROLL THE SCREEN PLAY-AREA    : Mouse movements or
                                   CD남 Joypad >> key and D-Pad movements
  ACTIVATE SELECTED WEAPON       : <Space Bar> or Joystick fire

  Note: CD남 Joypad's Red button, will do the same as Joystick's Fire
        button.

  BRING UP WEAPONS PANEL         : Mouse button or << CD남 Joypad button

  Once Weapons panel is active, click on the desired weapon or press
  joystick fire. Joystick L/R/U/D to move arrow (or use the mouse).

  CENTER IN ON CURRENT PLAYER    : <HELP> Key or >> + (BLUE) CD남 joypad
                                   b'ttons.

  CENTER IN ON SPECIFIC PLAYER
  AND DISPLAY ENERGY AT THE SAME : (1) for Player 1
  TIME                             (2) for Player 2

  QUIT BACK TO MAIN MENU         : (ESC) or Click the icon

  As you can see, I've done my best to clone the controls for "Worms",
  mainly because all you lot should be used to it by now and probably
  wouldn't feel confortable with any other controls!

  If you forget a control, try the same thing you'd do while playing
  "Worms" and with any luck, it'll work! Same goes with CD남 Joypad
  controls.


