                            T H E  M A I N  M E M U

   On the main menu options screen, we have the following options available
   to you, the public...


   START GAME:           Well, let's see now...it starts the game!

   ENTER PLAYER'S NAMES: Enter up to 8 Letter names for both players. This
                         will then display your name on the score table,
                         displayed at the end of each game and also during
                         the game, when your turn is about to commence.

   FULL VERSION:         How to get hold of the full game!
                         This option will be "SCORE OPTIONS" in the full
                         game!

   STATISTIC OPTIONS:    Beings up another panel with options, variables to
                         change, such as the amount of energy you start with
                         and the weapon amounts you begin with. Use the left
                         mouse button to add a value and right mouse button
                         to subtract.

   CREDITS:              The most important part of the game, no?

   QUIT:                 Exits back to DOS/Workbench.


